ays, positioning patients for safe eating, and monitoring patients for potential difficulties.  \n\n# Learning Objectives:  \n- Remembering the protocols for patient feeding \n- Understanding the importance of nutrition and safe feeding practices \n- Applying the correct techniques for assisting patients with eating \n- Analyzing the patient's ability to swallow and eat safely \n- Creating a supportive and respectful environment to enhance the patient's mealtime experience \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to assist patients with feeding efficiently and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Learn how to provide proper feeding assistance through interactive, hands-on practice."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holo Pundits", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7564952043613663"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "848890776576819"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "848890776576819"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1721737196, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "848890776576819"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {